568
00:54:21.591 --> 00:54:24.803
Oh. don't worry about it. I'm a boxer.
It'll take more than this to kill me.

569
00:54:24.886 --> 00:54:26.680
- It's fine.
- I'm sorry. I can't

570
00:54:26.763 --> 00:54:29.516
Listen to me.
